                                                <div class=flex-1>
                                                    <h4 class="font-bold text-red-700 mb-1">Terjadi Kesalahan</h4>
                                                    <p class="text-red-600 text-sm"></p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id=birthday-results-header
                                        class="hidden flex items-center justify-between mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-50 to-purple-50 p-4 rounded-xl border-2"
                                        style=border-color:#ec4899>
                                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold" style=color:#be185d><i
                                                class="fas fa-check-circle mr-2" style=color:#ec4899></i> <span
                                                id=birthday-results-count>6</span> Foto Ulang Tahun</h3><button
                                            id=birthday-download-all-btn
                                            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-600 to-purple-600 hover:from-pink-700 hover:to-purple-700 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-semibold shadow-lg transition transform hover:scale-105 flex items-center gap-2"><i
                                                class="fas fa-download"></i> <span class="hidden sm:inline">Download
                                                Semua</span></button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id=birthday-results-grid class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6"></div>
                                    <div id=birthday-empty-state
                                        class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-12 text-center border-2 border-dashed"
                                        style=border-color:#ec4899><i class="fas fa-birthday-cake text-6xl mb-4"
                                            style=color:#ec4899></i>
                                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3" style=color:#be185d>Siap Membuat Foto Ulang
                                            Tahun</h3>
                                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 max-w-md mx-auto">Upload foto, pilih kategori umur
                                            dan tema yang sesuai, lalu klik generate untuk membuat foto ulang tahun yang
