                            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Ubah produk apapun jadi foto mirror
                                selfie yang aesthetic! Upload produk, pilih style, dan dapatkan hasil seperti mirror
                                selfie yang keren.</p>
                        </header>
                        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8">
                            <div class="w-full lg:w-5/12 flex-shrink-0">
                                <div class="card sticky top-6">
                                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
                                        <div>
                                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                                                <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full text-white font-bold text-sm shadow-lg"
                                                    style=background:linear-gradient(135deg,#06b6d4,#0284c1)>1</div>
