                            </div><textarea id=vehicle-custom-description rows=3
                                placeholder="Contoh: Tambahkan wide body kit agresif, cat hitam matte dengan racing stripes merah, velg racing 19 inch, dll..."
                                class="w-full px-4 py-3 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:border-red-500 focus:outline-none resize-none"></textarea>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">Deskripsikan modifikasi spesifik yang Anda inginkan
                                untuk hasil yang lebih akurat</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-6 md:p-8 mb-6">
                            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                                <div
                                    class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500 to-red-600 text-white font-bold text-sm shadow-lg mr-3">
                                    6</div>
                                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Aspect Ratio</h2>
                            </div>
                            <div id=vehicle-aspect-selection class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3"><button type=button
                                    data-aspect=16:9 class="option-btn-vehicle selected">
                                    <div class=font-semibold>16:9 Landscape</div>
                                </button> <button type=button data-aspect=1:1 class=option-btn-vehicle>
                                    <div class=font-semibold>1:1 Square</div>
                                </button> <button type=button data-aspect=9:16 class=option-btn-vehicle>
                                    <div class=font-semibold>9:16 Story</div>
                                </button></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-6 md:p-8 mb-6">
                            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                                <div
                                    class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500 to-red-600 text-white font-bold text-sm shadow-lg mr-3">
                                    7</div>
                                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Number of Variations</h2>
                            </div>
                            <div id=vehicle-count-selection class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3"><button type=button
                                    data-count=3 class=count-btn-vehicle>3 Variations</button> <button type=button
                                    data-count=4 class="count-btn-vehicle count-selected">4 Variations</button> <button
                                    type=button data-count=6 class=count-btn-vehicle>6 Variations</button></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-6 md:p-8 mb-6">
                            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                                <div
                                    class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500 to-red-600 text-white font-bold text-sm shadow-lg mr-3">
                                    8</div>
                                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Generate Modified Vehicles</h2>
                            </div><button id=vehicle-generate-btn disabled=disabled
                                class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 hover:from-red-700 hover:to-red-800 disabled:from-gray-400 disabled:to-gray-500 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.02] disabled:hover:scale-100 disabled:cursor-not-allowed text-lg"><i
                                    class="fas fa-magic mr-2"></i> Generate <span id=vehicle-count-text>4</span>
                                Modified Versions</button>
                        </div>
                        <div id=vehicle-error-message
                            class="hidden bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-4 mb-6 rounded-lg">
                            <div class="flex items-center"><i
                                    class="fas fa-exclamation-circle text-red-500 text-xl mr-3"></i>
                                <p id=vehicle-error-text class="text-red-700 font-semibold"></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id=vehicle-loading-indicator
                            class="hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-red-50 to-red-100 rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 mb-6">
                            <div class=text-center>
                                <div
                                    class="inline-block animate-spin rounded-full h-16 w-16 border-b-4 border-red-600 mb-4">
                                </div>
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2"><i
                                        class="fas fa-wand-magic-sparkles mr-2 text-red-600"></i> <span
                                        id=vehicle-loading-text>Modifying vehicle...</span></h3>
                                <div class="mt-4 bg-white rounded-full h-3 overflow-hidden shadow-inner">
                                    <div id=vehicle-progress-bar
                                        class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-red-600 h-full transition-all duration-500 rounded-full"
                                        style=width:0%></div>
                                </div>
                                <p id=vehicle-progress-text class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">0/4</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id=vehicle-results-section class="hidden bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-6 md:p-8 mb-6">
                            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-6">
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 md:mb-0"><i
                                        class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mr-2"></i> <span
                                        id=vehicle-results-count>4</span> Modified Versions Generated!</h3><button
                                    id=vehicle-download-all-btn
                                    class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 hover:from-red-700 hover:to-red-800 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"><i
                                        class="fas fa-download mr-2"></i> Download All</button>
                            </div>
                            <div id=vehicle-results-grid class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id=vehicle-empty-state
                            class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-red-100 rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-12">
                            <div class="text-center text-gray-500">
                                <div
                                    class="inline-block p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-100 to-red-200 rounded-full mb-4">
                                    <i class="fas fa-car text-6xl text-red-400"></i>
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-lg font-semibold">AI Vehicle Modifier</p>
                                <p class=text-sm>Upload kendaraan dan pilih modifikasi yang diinginkan</p>
                                <div class="mt-6 bg-red-50 rounded-lg p-4 max-w-md mx-auto">
                                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 text-left"><strong
                                            class=text-red-600>Fitur:</strong><br>✓ Modifikasi mobil & motor dengan
                                        AI<br>✓ 8 kategori: Body kit, Wheels, Paint, Lowering, Spoiler, Lighting,
                                        Interior, Full Custom<br>✓ 8 styles: JDM, VIP, Racing, Stance, Off-road,
                                        Classic, Modern, Custom<br>✓ Custom description untuk modifikasi spesifik<br>✓
                                        Perfect untuk visualisasi modifikasi kendaraan</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>
        </div>
        <div id="mobile-nav-placeholder"></div>
    </div>
    <script type="module" src="js/main.js"></script>
    <script src="js/auth.js"></script>
</body>

</html>